<br>
Back to the point. If you are going to ask me to help and I agree, it would be nice if you'd show some respect.<br>
<br>
I do not expect to leave what I'm doing to spend 40 minutes travelling half way across Norath, then sit around for another 40 minutes, only to find you've been sitting in an exp group the whole time, and are in no hurry to leave.<br>
<br>
If you won't need help for another 2 hours, tell me so I don't waste my time, and at least pretend to be making some sort of effort to arrange it, i.e. getting people to the spot, meaning you'd actually have to leave your group and *gasp* go there.<br>
<br>
It also helps if you have some sort of clue about what you have to be doing. <p><font size=2><font color=blue><a href=http://nightwatchers.dpn.ch/eq_view_profile.html?num=1190>Chubbylumpkins Anklesbane</a></font></font>
